# ─── Database ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Use the Transaction pooler URL (port 6543) — required for Supabase serverless.
# Found in: Supabase dashboard → Project Settings → Database → Connection string → Transaction
# Format: postgres://postgres.PROJECT_REF:PASSWORD@aws-0-REGION.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres
